manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: HD Emulator Video Game Console for TV PC Unlike normal handheld game console, YRPRSODF wireless video game system is motion sensor design. Just hold the 2.4G wireless gamepad on hand and wave the game remote controller or move your body, the game system will sense it automatically and you can play games with role of virtual person in the video or the real person. which give you a immersive gaming experience. Best toy gift for kids age 4-8, 6-8, 8-10, 8-12, boys & girls, teens and adults. Comes with 63 interactive games + 820 retro games: 31 motion interactive games: Running, Fishing,Baseketball, Football,Jumping etc. 32 puzzle games: memory, pairing games etc. 820 retro games: classic retro games such as 80s, 90s childhood games. What you can benefits from playing these games? 1. Interactive with kids and parents, keep good relationship with family. 2. Developing children's intelligence. 3. Help to distract children, keep them busy and improve their bad habits. 4. Doing exercise without going out. 5. Entertaining and relaxing at home. Note: when you want to exit from playing the retro games, please enter to the main playing interface of the retro games(The final step setting of retro games and start playing the retro games) and press " Back" key for 3 second to exit. It won't exit if you press the " Back" key on main menu of retro games(Just enter to retro game menu).

2.4G Wireless Game Controller YRPRSODF 2 player somatosensory game console comes with 2pcs portable 2.4G wireless game handle, high transmission signal and high sensitivity which will response quickly and correctly. reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Couldn't play games
reviews.reviewText: I had no problem setting this up and selecting games, so the controller works, but none of the games I tried responded to the controller. I also brought another one for our Church's Wednesday Night Live Event where we play a variety of games but I'm in charge of keeping the preteens engaged. The $60 price tag, easy to setup, and the almost endless number of games make this purchase a no brainer.
